ğŸŒ Core Concept
Institutions (schools, HR departments, financial firms, etc.) often request and receive documents via emailâ€”ID proofs, forms, reports, certificates, etc. These exchanges are typically unstructured, repetitive, and error-prone.
Our web app acts as the automation layer between email communication and document storage.
When an institution connects its email account, the platform automatically:
1.	Tracks requests and responses sent to users or employees.
2.	Parses incoming emails for attachments and metadata.
3.	Organizes and stores documents in the right cloud storage location (e.g., per user, department, or project folder).
4.	Maintains an audit trail of all document exchanges for compliance and tracking.
 
